 LaserPhoto GO1 By TAD BARTIMUS Associated Press Writer VALDEZ, Alaska (AP) Exxon crews Tuesday finished pumping the remaining crude oil out of the tanker Exxon Valdez in preparation for refloating and removing the source of the nation's worst-ever oil spill.
